  respective report authors, the participating programs, and HackerOne, Inc.

Nature of this copy
-------------------
  - This is a point-in-time archival mirror (source data circa 2021, ending around
    HackerOne report ID ~1,002,000).
  - It is NOT maintained or kept current.
  - It aggregates only publicly disclosed metadata (report URLs and public titles).
    It contains no private report content, no personal data beyond public report
    titles, and no credentials, secrets, or tracking code.

